title: DPS BestOf
itunes:title: DPS BestOf
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses what story line could come out of the 2022 NFL Draft. Has a new candidate for the no.1 overall pick emerged? Jeff Van Gundy calls in to recap all the action from the NBA Playoffs. And Peter King shares where he thinks Deebo Samuel will land.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
